Description
  TJvAppDBStorage inherits from TJvCustomAppDBStorage and publishes all of it's properties and events
  but does not introduce any new behavior.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCustomAppDBStorage
Summary
  Storage component that reads and writes to a dataset.
Description
  TJvCustomAppDBStorage is a data storage backend that reads and writes the data to a dataset.

  As a descendant of TJvCustomAppStorage it provides the standard interface for storing data (such as
  settings, form positions and sizes, etc) in a dataset.

  The component introduces and publishes several new properties: DataSource, to indicate the dataset
  used for storage, SectionField, KeyField and ValueField that indicates the fields in the dataset to
  use to \read and \write the data.

  A dataset used with TJvCustomAppDBStorage must be updateable (i.e not readonly), support the
  TDataset.Locate standard search method and support bookmarks. Although not required, it is
  recommended (if possible) to create an index on the fields used for the section and key name
  (SectionFiald and KeyField, respectively).

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCustomAppDBStorage.DataSource
Summary
  Links the storage to a dataset.
Description
  Specify the data source component that identifies the dataset in which the target fields are found.
  To allow the storage to represent the data for the fields, both the DataSource and the SectionField,
  KeyField and ValueField properties must be set.

  If DataSource is nil, use the OnRead and OnWrite events to \read and \write data.
See Also
  TJvCustomAppDBStorage.KeyField, TJvCustomAppDBStorage.OnRead, TJvCustomAppDBStorage.OnWrite,
  TJvCustomAppDBStorage.SectionField, TJvCustomAppDBStorage.ValueField

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCustomAppDBStorage.KeyField
Summary
  Identifies the field from which the storage reads and writes key names.
Description
  Set KeyField to indicate which field in the dataset is used to store key names.
See Also
  TJvCustomAppDBStorage.DataSource, TJvCustomAppDBStorage.SectionField,
  TJvCustomAppDBStorage.ValueField

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCustomAppDBStorage.OnRead
Summary
  Occurs when data is read.
Description
  Write a handler for the OnRead event to take specific action when data is read from storage. You can
  use OnRead even if DataSource or any of the fields are unassigned.
Parameters
  Sender  - The TJvCustomAppDBStorage that called the event.
  Section - The name of the section to read.
  Key     - The name of the key to read.
  Value   - The value that was read.
See Also
  TJvCustomAppDBStorage.OnWrite

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCustomAppDBStorage.OnWrite
Summary
  Occurs when data is written.
Description
  Write a handler for the OnWrite event to take specific action when data is written to storage. You
  can use OnWrite even if DataSource or any of the fields are unassigned.
Parameters
  Sender  - The TJvCustomAppDBStorage that called the event.
  Section - The name of the section to write to. If it doesn't exist, it will be created.
  Key     - The name of the key to write to. If it doesn't exist, it will be created.
  Value   - The value to write.
See Also
  TJvCustomAppDBStorage.OnRead

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCustomAppDBStorage.SectionField
Summary
  Identifies the field from which the storage reads and writes the section name.
Description
  Set SectionField to indicate which field the dataset is used to store section names.
See Also
  TJvCustomAppDBStorage.DataSource, TJvCustomAppDBStorage.KeyField, TJvCustomAppDBStorage.ValueField

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCustomAppDBStorage.ValueField
Summary
  Identifies the field from which the storage reads and writes value data.
Description
  Set ValueField to indicate which field the dataset is used to store value data.
See Also
  TJvCustomAppDBStorage.DataSource, TJvCustomAppDBStorage.KeyField, TJvCustomAppDBStorage.SectionField

